data.description:
Hard to find acreage bordering the banks of the Roaring Fork River. Amazing potential on this 4.92 irrigated acres with home, utilities, two wells and septic in place. Mature shade and pine trees, 4 pastures with livestock and hay sheds, iron pipe corrals, wood board fence, small animal pens, raised garden area, raspberry bushes, and more. Walk the private trail along the river and view wildlife, catch some fish, or relax and listen to the crystal waters rushing over the rocks. The home is two story, 2828 sq ft, 4 bedrooms, 3 bath, with decks and access to the surrounding
cedar and pine covered red hills and river. This property is located within minutes of the
